Class GenericEdgeSet<T extends Edge>

All Implemented Interfaces:
EdgeSet<T>, Serializable, Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, Set<T>
public class GenericEdgeSet<T extends Edge>
extends AbstractSet<T>
implements EdgeSet<T>, Serializable

An EdgeSet implementation that imposes no restrictions on the type of edges that may be contained within. This class keeps track of which vertices are in the set as well, allowing for efficient vertex-based operations.

Author:
David Jurgens
